bodyTemplate:
Hi {{contact.agentName}},

I wanted to introduce myself — I'm actively looking for a property in {{criteria.areaFocus}} and would like to register with you so you can alert me when something suitable comes on.

What I'm looking for:
- {{criteria.beds}}-bed freehold, ideally {{criteria.propertyType}}
- Budget up to £{{criteria.budget}}
- Must-haves: {{criteria.mustHaves}}
- Target move: {{finances.goal.movingWindow}}

My position: first-time buyer, chain-free, AIP in place for £{{finances.aipAmount}}. I'm proceedable now.

Please do keep me on your list — I reply promptly and I'm serious about moving. My mobile is {{profile.mobile}}.

Thanks,
{{profile.firstName}} {{profile.lastName}}
{{profile.mobile}} · {{profile.email}}

Dear {{contact.agentName}},

Thank you for coming back to me regarding {{listing.address}}.

Having considered the counter-offer of £{{listing.counterOfferAmount}}, my response is as follows:

{{counterOfferResponse}}

My position remains unchanged — first-time buyer, chain-free, AIP in place. I can proceed quickly if we can reach an agreement.

Please pass this response to the seller and confirm receipt.

Best regards,
{{profile.firstName}} {{profile.lastName}}
{{profile.mobile}} · {{profile.email}}

Hi {{contact.brokerName}},

Great news — my offer of £{{listing.agreedPrice}} on {{listing.address}} has been accepted. Please proceed with the full mortgage application.

Key details:
- Property: {{listing.address}}
- Purchase price: £{{listing.agreedPrice}}
- Tenure: {{listing.tenure}}
- Target exchange: 8–12 weeks from today ({{offerAcceptedDate}})

My solicitor is:
{{contact.solicitorFirm}}
{{contact.solicitorEmail}}
{{contact.solicitorPhone}}

Please liaise with them directly as needed. Let me know what you need from me to get the application submitted.

Thanks,
{{profile.firstName}} {{profile.lastName}}
{{profile.mobile}}

Dear {{contact.solicitorName}},

I'd like to formally instruct {{contact.solicitorFirm}} to act on my behalf in the purchase of {{listing.address}} at the agreed price of £{{listing.agreedPrice}}.

My details:
- Full name: {{profile.firstName}} {{profile.lastName}}
- Date of birth: {{profile.dob}}
- Mobile: {{profile.mobile}}
- Email: {{profile.email}}
- Current address: {{profile.address}}

Property details:
- Address: {{listing.address}}
- Tenure: {{listing.tenure}}
- Agreed price: £{{listing.agreedPrice}}
- Seller's solicitor (if known): {{listing.sellerSolicitor}}
- Selling agent: {{contact.agentName}}, {{contact.agentEmail}}, {{contact.agentPhone}}

Mortgage:
- Lender: {{finances.aipLender}}
- Deposit source: {{finances.depositSource}}
- Broker: {{contact.brokerName}}, {{contact.brokerEmail}}

Target exchange: 8–12 weeks from acceptance ({{offerAcceptedDate}}).

Please send your client care letter and I will sign and return it promptly.

Kind regards,
{{profile.firstName}} {{profile.lastName}}
{{profile.mobile}} · {{profile.email}}

Hi {{contact.surveyorName}},

Thank you for your quote — I'd like to go ahead and book a RICS Level 2 HomeBuyer Report on {{listing.address}} at the agreed fee of £{{surveyFee}}.

Preferred dates (in order of preference):
1. {{surveyDateOption1}}
2. {{surveyDateOption2}}

Access is via the selling agent:
- {{contact.agentName}}, {{contact.agentPhone}}, {{contact.agentEmail}}

Please liaise with them directly to confirm entry. I'll let them know to expect your call.

I look forward to receiving the report within {{surveyTurnaround}} days of inspection.

Thanks,
{{profile.firstName}} {{profile.lastName}}
{{profile.mobile}} · {{profile.email}}

Hi {{contact.agentName}},

To help you prepare the memorandum of sale for {{listing.address}}, here are my solicitor and mortgage broker details:

Solicitor / conveyancer:
- {{contact.solicitorFirm}}
- {{contact.solicitorName}}
- {{contact.solicitorEmail}} · {{contact.solicitorPhone}}

Mortgage broker:
- {{contact.brokerName}}
- {{contact.brokerEmail}} · {{contact.brokerPhone}}

Please let me know if you need anything else to proceed.

Kind regards,
{{profile.firstName}} {{profile.lastName}}
{{profile.mobile}}

Hi {{contact.surveyorName}},

Thank you for the report on {{listing.address}}. I've read it carefully and have a few follow-up questions I'd appreciate 15 minutes to discuss.

My main questions are:
{{surveyQuestions}}

Could we arrange a brief call this week or next? I'm available most mornings and most weekday evenings after 6pm.

Thanks,
{{profile.firstName}} {{profile.lastName}}
{{profile.mobile}}

Dear {{contact.agentName}},

Thank you for all the progress so far on {{listing.address}}. Following my RICS Level 2 HomeBuyer Report I need to raise a concern.

The survey has identified the following issues:
{{surveyFindings}}

My surveyor has estimated remediation costs of approximately £{{surveyRemediationCost}}. In light of this, I'd like to revise my offer to £{{listing.revisedOfferAmount}}.

I remain committed to the purchase and keen to exchange as planned. I hope we can resolve this quickly. Please pass this to the seller and confirm receipt.

Best regards,
{{profile.firstName}} {{profile.lastName}}
{{profile.mobile}} · {{profile.email}}

Hi,

I'd like a buildings insurance quote for a property I'm purchasing.

Property details:
- Address: {{listing.address}}
- Property type: {{listing.propertyType}}, {{listing.beds}}-bed.
- Construction: {{listing.construction}}
- Rebuild cost (from RICS Level 2 survey): £{{listing.rebuildCost}}
- Cover required from: {{targetExchangeDate}} (exchange date — lender requirement)

About me:
- Date of birth: {{profile.dob}}
- No claims in past 5 years.
- Mobile: {{profile.mobile}}

Mortgage lender: {{finances.aipLender}} — please confirm your policy is acceptable to them.

Many thanks,
{{profile.firstName}} {{profile.lastName}}

To whom it may concern,

I am writing to notify you of a change of occupier at {{listing.address}}, effective {{targetCompletionDate}}.

New occupier details:
- Name: {{profile.firstName}} {{profile.lastName}}
- Contact: {{profile.mobile}} · {{profile.email}}
- Correspondence address from {{targetCompletionDate}}: {{listing.address}}

Meter readings taken on {{targetCompletionDate}}:
- Gas: {{meterReadingGas}}
- Electricity: {{meterReadingElec}}
- Water: {{meterReadingWater}}

Previous account details (if known): account held in seller's name.

Please set up an account in my name from {{targetCompletionDate}} using the above readings as the opening read, and send my first bill to {{profile.email}}.

Thank you,
{{profile.firstName}} {{profile.lastName}}
{{profile.mobile}}
